<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="compensate-v">compensate <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kɒmpenseɪt/    美 /'kɑːmpenseɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>补偿；弥补；赔偿：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Nothing can <strong>compensate for</strong> the loss of time. 
光阴一去不复返。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I suggest that you also <strong>compensate me for</strong> the injuries that I have received. 
我认为你还要对我所受的伤害进行赔偿。</p><footer>北师大⑧ – 23</footer></div></div>